data.description: THIS HOME IS A MUST SEE!!! Beautiful home located in the west end of Beaumont. This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths with 2175 square feet situated at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. This home has a Large Open Floor Plan with lots of space for all your family gatherings. Luxury tile flooring throughout, high ceilings in living room, gas fireplace. Kitchen includes granite counter tops, gas stove, oversized island with lots of seating and storage with beautiful finishings. The primary features a custom shower, large soaking tub, dual vanities, and organized closet space. A bonus room with a half bath is also provided upstairs, and could be used as an extra bedroom, guest suite, home gym, or a media space. Large back yard with a covered patio. Great neighborhood close to shopping and entertainment. Schedule your showing today!!
